hopobject.body: How do you do? medisuisse.net bewertung It’s not only about the newcomers, though. John Donahoe, CEO of eBay, gave a fascinating exposition on the opportunities and challenges of reacting to innovation as a major, global incumbent. eBay was a start-up a few years ago, too; not losing that entrepreneurial spirit is a key strategic priority. Acquisitions and “acqui-hires” – where larger companies acquire teams rather than the assets of a start-up, often when the start-up itself has failed – are one way to do this.
